♪All my efforts♪

210
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:42,460
♪Are not worth it in your mind♪

211
00:13:43,460 --> 00:13:45,500
♪It doesn't matter if it's nighttime♪

212
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:47,180
♪The separation is inevitable♪

213
